        {
          "function": "RestyleManager::ProcessRestyledFrames(nsStyleChangeList&)",
          "file": "layout/style/RestyleManager.cpp",
          "line": 1548,
          "role": "Iterates the nsStyleChangeList. For each (frame, hint) pair, dispatches the appropriate action: nsChangeHint_ReflowHintsForISizeChange → FrameNeedsReflow(); nsChangeHint_RepaintFrame → frame->InvalidateFrameSubtree(); nsChangeHint_UpdateTransformLayer → ApplyRenderingChangeToTree(); nsChangeHint_ReconstructFrame → frame constructor rebuild."
