          "function": "RestyleManager::ApplyRenderingChangeToTree(nsIFrame*, nsChangeHint)",
          "file": "layout/style/RestyleManager.cpp",
          "line": 1268,
          "role": "Handles paint-only change hints (opacity, transform, visibility). Calls DoApplyRenderingChangeToTree() which sets NS_FRAME_UPDATE_LAYER_TREE and calls InvalidateFrameSubtree()."
